Class Notification

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.iland.core.api.vcd.Notification
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Notification
extends Object
implements Serializable
    VCD Notification implementation.

    Parses XML payload and extracting information. Generic for all VCD notification types.

    Author:
    Julien Anguenot

      • getProcessed

        public boolean getProcessed()
        Returns if whether or not this notification has been processed by the system.

        Notifications, after being stored, must be post-processed to reconnect to VCD and gather information about the actual information included in alert.

        Returns:
        true or false. False by default
